metadata.name: Reading a book #512
metadata.description:
The formal structure of a book is beautiful by itself, but its aesthetic is the tacit atmosphere within which events take place in a story.

The WebGL real-time animation sets up an initial grid based on the fxhash. The grid cells get subdivided into another grid and the resulting cells become filled with pixels in color (~33%) or black and white (~66%).
The colored pixels come in 3 different coloring styles.
- Big Palette (~49%)
- Small Palette (~49%)
- Monochrome [b/w] (~2%)
4 noise algorithms modify the pixels of selected grid cells while at the same time 4 reset algorithms reassemble the initial image. The selected cells switch over time.

metadata.name: Humanity #31
metadata.description:
In a modern society everyone tries to dictate his own rules of life, where is no place for emotions and sincere feelings. Those concrete jungles are more like giant anthills.
People are interchangeable gears in one big mechanism, today you are here and tomorrow.. who knows. Tomorrow you could be gone.

New element, same functionality, you won`t find something new. Humanity is on the right path to globalization and unification. We are entitled to agreed points.
You can`t be who you are. Sooner or later, you`re going to have to be an interchangeable element. 
The rules of this life have been written for you.

Polina Arz ©
